{"word":"Isaac","slug":"isaac","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Isaac</b> <a href=\"#/H3327\">H3327</a><br/><a href=\"#/H3446\">H3446</a> <br/> 1. Son of Abraham:<br/> - Miraculous birth<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=17&verse=19'>Gen 17:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=18&verse=15'>Gen 18:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=8'>Gen 21:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=24&verse=3'>Jos 24:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=1&verse=28'>1Ch 1:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=4&verse=28'>Gal 4:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=11&verse=11'>Heb 11:11</a> <br/> - Ancestor of Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=1&verse=2'>Mat 1:2</a> <br/> - Offered in sacrifice by his father<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=22&verse=19'>Gen 22:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=11&verse=17'>Heb 11:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=59&chapter=2&verse=21'>Jas 2:21</a> <br/> - Is provided a wife from among his kindred<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24'>Gen 24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=20'>Gen 25:20</a> <br/> - Abrahamic covenant confirmed in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=26&verse=5'>Gen 26:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=16&verse=19'>1Ch 16:19</a> <br/> - Dwells in the south country at the well Lahai-Roi<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=62'>Gen 24:62</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=11'>Gen 25:11</a> <br/> - With Ishmael, buries his father in the cave of Machpelah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=9'>Gen 25:9</a> <br/> - Esau and Jacob born to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=26'>Gen 25:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=1&verse=34'>1Ch 1:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=24&verse=4'>Jos 24:4</a> <br/> - Dwells in Gerar<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=26&verse=11'>Gen 26:11</a> <br/> - Prospers<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=26&verse=14'>Gen 26:14</a> <br/> - Possesses large flocks and herds<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=26&verse=14'>Gen 26:14</a> <br/> - Digs wells, and is defrauded of them by the herdsmen of Abimelech<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=26&verse=15'>Gen 26:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=26&verse=21'>Gen 26:21</a> <br/> - Removes to the valley of Gerar, afterward called Beer-Sheba<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=26&verse=33'>Gen 26:33</a> <br/> - His old age, last blessing upon his sons<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=27&verse=40'>Gen 27:40</a> <br/> - Death and burial of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=35&verse=29'>Gen 35:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=49&verse=31'>Gen 49:31</a> <br/> - His filial obedience<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=22&verse=9'>Gen 22:9</a> <br/> - His peaceableness<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=26&verse=22'>Gen 26:22</a> <br/> - Was a prophet<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=27&verse=29'>Gen 27:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=27&verse=38'>Gen 27:38</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=27&verse=40'>Gen 27:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=11&verse=20'>Heb 11:20</a> <br/> - His devoutness<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=63'>Gen 24:63</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=21'>Gen 25:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=26&verse=25'>Gen 26:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=8&verse=11'>Mat 8:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=13&verse=28'>Luk 13:28</a> <br/> - Prophecies concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=17&verse=21'>Gen 17:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=18&verse=14'>Gen 18:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=12'>Gen 21:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=26&verse=5'>Gen 26:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=26&verse=24'>Gen 26:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=32&verse=13'>Exo 32:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=16&verse=16'>1Ch 16:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=9&verse=7'>Rom 9:7</a> <br/> 2. A designation of the ten tribes<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=7&verse=9'>Amo 7:9</a>"}]}